{"tid":813714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚耀宗爆偉論：港青談港獨 因想令自己好威變紅人","createTime":"2018-09-10T16:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T01:39:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"839859ccb223b21ddc3f00a4654314cba58ed539","tid":813714,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180909/large/1536476707_680b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180909%2Flarge%2F1536476707_680b.png&h=4fbaf272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》23條未立法，港府與建制派已不斷打壓討論港獨的言論自由。全國人大常委、民建聯會務顧問譚耀宗今在TVB節目《講清講楚》中說，聽到大學生討論港獨令他感到憤怒，指年輕人想挑戰權威，引來傳媒追訪，令自己「好威」和「變紅人」，年輕人談港獨亦證明他們對中國歷史不了解和沒有感情，「所以我覺得一講到港獨唔係言論自由嘅問題，港獨係分裂國土。係出賣香港人、出賣香港」。<br />\n<br />\n對於資深大律師湯家驊曾指，社會應容許理性和學術討論港獨議題，譚耀宗回應強調，不需要討論港獨，「睇唔到有咩討論價值」。他指，2003年23條立法時尚未有人討論港獨，但近年已有組織打正旗號支持港獨，認為社會應予以港獨更多批評和譴責，而現屆政府亦應就23條立法做好準備，需要立法時就「水到渠成」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，港人本月起可申請內地居住證，但稅務問題未釐清。譚承認稅務問題會影響港人申證意欲，但籲港人無需擔心，相信有關問題之後可得到處理，又認為最理想做法是港人在「境外」得益只納香港稅，強調內地居住證只是「（國家）想畀方便香港人，唔係想與此同時收到我哋啲稅」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180909/58661795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180909%2F58661795&d=oJvLZC8ezx0FqvPelps3Gv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d8a99f23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180909%2F58661795&h=1608cebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180909/58661795</a>"},{"pid":"64ce65d262eb661933641e069f2dbcdd357b99d1","tid":813714,"uid":41914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:15:04.000Z","msg":"呢D人思想已經離晒地......."},{"pid":"bc6719cb90385a07dd86e15c9e8cd315ff3601de","tid":813714,"uid":37528,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"講緊梁柒首？"},{"pid":"ebfcc2742e851e0252882a97f130d17fbcda1f3c","tid":813714,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc6719cb90385a07dd86e15c9e8cd315ff3601de","tid":813714,"uid":37528,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"講緊梁柒首？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:34:46.000Z","msg":"前特首反港獨, 因想奶中共鞋底免被起訴"},{"pid":"9ca297db453933c3997d3dd3baf669f1266c7a06","tid":813714,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"其實悶唔悶左d<br />\n香港無得被精神病<br />\n來來去去都係人格媒殺<br />\n<br />\n馬總統看手錶式新聞<br />\n講下失業呀愛情史呀<br />\n<br />\n我以為睇緊cctvb"},{"pid":"c64ab0667fc9fc1ee7ed5a85c29dafe2671b8078","tid":813714,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:15:48.000Z","msg":"你做人大咪又係因為木威<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1da558ff87b07127763fe86da963326353f998f","tid":813714,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"你班廢老日日反港獨咪又係搏上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過氣啦，收皮啦"},{"pid":"2ffcbc4b62fc5741914765c467225727d9810f9d","tid":813714,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}